{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"It's not about technology,"},{"time":2000,"text":"it's about people and stories."},{"time":4000,"text":"I could show you"},{"time":6000,"text":"what recently was on television"},{"time":8000,"text":"as a high quality video:"},{"time":10000,"text":"60 Minutes, many of you may have seen it."},{"time":13000,"text":"And it was the now director of the entire piece"},{"time":16000,"text":"of the veteran's administration --"},{"time":19000,"text":"who, himself, had lost an arm 39 years ago"},{"time":22000,"text":"in Vietnam --"},{"time":25000,"text":"who was adamantly opposed to these crazy devices"},{"time":27000,"text":"that don't work."},{"time":30000,"text":"And it turns out that with 60 Minutes cameras rolling in the background,"},{"time":33000,"text":"after he pretty much made his position clear on this --"},{"time":36000,"text":"he had his hook and he had his --"},{"time":39000,"text":"he wore this arm for less than two hours"},{"time":42000,"text":"and was able to pour himself a drink and got quite emotional over the fact"},{"time":45000,"text":"that, quote -- his quote --"},{"time":48000,"text":"it's the first time he's felt like he's had an arm in 39 years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":52000,"text":"But that would sort of be jumping to the middle of the story,"},{"time":55000,"text":"and I'm not going to show you that polished video."},{"time":57000,"text":"I'm going to, instead, in a minute or two,"},{"time":59000,"text":"show you an early, crude video"},{"time":62000,"text":"because I think it's"},{"time":64000,"text":"a better way to tell a story."}]},{"cues":[{"time":68000,"text":"A few years ago I was visited by"},{"time":70000,"text":"the guy that runs DARPA,"},{"time":72000,"text":"the people that fund all the advanced technologies"},{"time":75000,"text":"that businesses and universities probably wouldn't take the risk of doing."},{"time":82000,"text":"They have a particular interest in ones that will help our soldiers."},{"time":86000,"text":"I get this sort of unrequested -- by me anyway -- visit,"},{"time":91000,"text":"and sitting in my conference room is a very senior surgeon"},{"time":94000,"text":"from the military"},{"time":96000,"text":"and the guy that runs DARPA."}]},{"cues":[{"time":100000,"text":"They proceed to tell me a story which comes down"},{"time":103000,"text":"to basically the following. We have used such advanced technologies"},{"time":106000,"text":"now and made them available"},{"time":109000,"text":"in the most remote places that we put soldiers:"},{"time":112000,"text":"hills of Afghanistan, Iraq ..."},{"time":116000,"text":"They were quite proud of the fact that"},{"time":118000,"text":"you know, before the dust clears,"},{"time":121000,"text":"if some soldier has been hurt"},{"time":123000,"text":"they will have collected him or her, they will have brought him back,"},{"time":126000,"text":"they will be getting world-class triage emergency care"},{"time":129000,"text":"faster than you and I would be getting it if we were hurt"},{"time":133000,"text":"in a car accident in a major city in the United States."},{"time":137000,"text":"That's the good news."}]},{"cues":[{"time":139000,"text":"The bad news is if they've collected this person"},{"time":142000,"text":"and he or she is missing an arm or leg,"},{"time":145000,"text":"part of the face, it's probably not coming back."},{"time":149000,"text":"So, they started giving me the statistics on how many of these kids had lost an arm."},{"time":153000,"text":"And then the surgeon pointed out, with a lot of anger,"},{"time":156000,"text":"he said, \"Why is it? At the end of the Civil War,"},{"time":160000,"text":"they were shooting each other with muskets. If somebody lost an arm,"},{"time":162000,"text":"we gave them a wooden stick with a hook on it."},{"time":167000,"text":"Now we've got F18s and F22s,"},{"time":170000,"text":"and if somebody loses an arm,"},{"time":172000,"text":"we give them a plastic stick with a hook on it.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":175000,"text":"And they basically said, \"This is unacceptable,\""},{"time":179000,"text":"and then the punchline: \"So, Dean,"},{"time":181000,"text":"we're here because you make medical stuff."},{"time":183000,"text":"You're going to give us an arm.\""},{"time":186000,"text":"And I was waiting for the 500 pages of bureaucracy,"},{"time":189000,"text":"paperwork and DODs."},{"time":192000,"text":"No, the guy says,"},{"time":195000,"text":"\"We're going to bring a guy into this conference room,"},{"time":199000,"text":"and wearing the arm you're going to give us,"},{"time":202000,"text":"he or she is going to pick up a raisin or a grape"},{"time":204000,"text":"off this table."},{"time":206000,"text":"If it's the grape, they won't break it.\""},{"time":209000,"text":"Great he needs efferent, afferent, haptic response sensors."},{"time":212000,"text":"\"If it's the raisin, they won't drop it.\""},{"time":215000,"text":"So he wants fine motor control: flex at the wrist,"},{"time":220000,"text":"flex at the elbow, abduct and flex at the shoulder."},{"time":224000,"text":"Either way they were going to eat it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":226000,"text":"\"Oh, by the way Dean. It's going to fit on a 50th percentile female frame --"},{"time":230000,"text":"namely 32 inches from the long finger --"},{"time":233000,"text":"and weigh less than nine pounds.\""},{"time":236000,"text":"50th percentile female frame."},{"time":239000,"text":"\"And it's going to be completely self contained including all its power.\""},{"time":243000,"text":"So, they finished that. And I, as you can tell,"},{"time":245000,"text":"am a bashful guy."},{"time":247000,"text":"I told them they're nuts."},{"time":249000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":251000,"text":"They've been watching too much \"Terminator.\""},{"time":253000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":255000,"text":"Then, the surgeon says to me,"},{"time":258000,"text":"\"Dean, you need to know"},{"time":261000,"text":"more than two dozen of these kids have come back"},{"time":264000,"text":"bilateral.\""},{"time":266000,"text":"Now, I cannot imagine --"},{"time":268000,"text":"I'm sorry, you may have a better"},{"time":272000,"text":"imagination than I do --"},{"time":274000,"text":"I can't imagine losing my arm,"},{"time":277000,"text":"and typically at 22 years old."},{"time":280000,"text":"But compared to that, losing two?"},{"time":283000,"text":"Seems like that would be an inconvenience."}]},{"cues":[{"time":287000,"text":"Anyway, I went home that night. I thought about it."},{"time":290000,"text":"I literally could not sleep"},{"time":292000,"text":"thinking about, \"I wonder how you'd roll over"},{"time":294000,"text":"with no shoulders.\""},{"time":298000,"text":"So, I decided we've got to do this."},{"time":301000,"text":"And trust me, I've got a day job, I've got a lot of day jobs."},{"time":303000,"text":"Most of my day job keeps me busy"},{"time":306000,"text":"funding my fantasies like FIRST and water and power ...."},{"time":308000,"text":"And I've got a lot of day jobs."},{"time":311000,"text":"But I figured I gotta do this."},{"time":315000,"text":"Did a little investigation,"},{"time":317000,"text":"went down to Washington, told them"},{"time":320000,"text":"I still think they're nuts but we're going to do it."},{"time":325000,"text":"And I told them I'd build them an arm."},{"time":327000,"text":"I told them it would probably take five years to get through the FDA,"},{"time":330000,"text":"and probably 10 years to be reasonably functional."},{"time":333000,"text":"Look what it takes to make things like iPods."},{"time":337000,"text":"\"Great,\" he said, \"You got two years.\""},{"time":340000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":341000,"text":"I said, \"I'll tell you what. I'll build you an arm"},{"time":343000,"text":"that's under nine pounds"},{"time":345000,"text":"that has all that capability in one year."},{"time":347000,"text":"It will take the other nine to make it functional and useful.\""},{"time":351000,"text":"We sort of agreed to disagree."}]},{"cues":[{"time":353000,"text":"I went back and I started putting a team together,"},{"time":355000,"text":"the best guys I could find with a passion to do this."},{"time":358000,"text":"At the end of exactly one year"},{"time":361000,"text":"we had a device with 14 degrees of freedom,"},{"time":363000,"text":"all the sensors, all the microprocessors,"},{"time":366000,"text":"all the stuff inside."},{"time":368000,"text":"I could show you it with a cosmesis on it"},{"time":370000,"text":"that's so real it's eerie, but then you wouldn't see"},{"time":372000,"text":"all this cool stuff."},{"time":375000,"text":"I then thought it would be years"},{"time":377000,"text":"before we'd be able to make it really, really useful."},{"time":382000,"text":"It turned out, as I think you could see"},{"time":384000,"text":"in Aimee's capabilities and attitudes,"},{"time":388000,"text":"people with a desire to do something"},{"time":391000,"text":"are quite remarkable and nature is quite adaptable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":395000,"text":"Anyway, with less than 10 hours of use,"},{"time":399000,"text":"two guys -- one that's bilateral."},{"time":403000,"text":"He's literally, he's got no shoulder on one side,"},{"time":406000,"text":"and he's high trans-humeral on the other."},{"time":408000,"text":"And that's Chuck and Randy together,"},{"time":413000,"text":"after 10 hours -- were playing in our office."},{"time":416000,"text":"And we took some pretty cruddy home movies."},{"time":420000,"text":"At the end of the one I'm going to show, it's only about a minute"},{"time":422000,"text":"and a couple of seconds long,"},{"time":427000,"text":"Chuck does something that to this day I'm jealous of,"},{"time":430000,"text":"I can't do it."},{"time":432000,"text":"He picks up a spoon, picks it up,"},{"time":434000,"text":"scoops out some Shredded Wheat and milk,"},{"time":438000,"text":"holds the spoon level"},{"time":440000,"text":"as he translates it, moving all these joints simultaneously,"},{"time":443000,"text":"to his mouth, and he doesn't drop any milk."},{"time":446000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":447000,"text":"I cannot do that."},{"time":449000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":451000,"text":"His wife was standing behind me."},{"time":453000,"text":"She's standing behind me at the time"},{"time":455000,"text":"and she says, \"Dean,"},{"time":458000,"text":"Chuck hasn't fed himself in 19 years."},{"time":462000,"text":"So, you've got a choice:"},{"time":464000,"text":"We keep the arm, or you keep Chuck.\""},{"time":466000,"text":"(Laughter) (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":469000,"text":"So, can we see that?"},{"time":479000,"text":"This is Chuck showing simultaneous control"},{"time":481000,"text":"of all the joints."},{"time":483000,"text":"He's punching our controls guy. The guy behind him"},{"time":485000,"text":"is our engineer/surgeon,"},{"time":487000,"text":"which is a convenient guy to have around."},{"time":491000,"text":"There's Randy, these guys are passing a rubber"},{"time":494000,"text":"little puck between them."},{"time":497000,"text":"And just as in the spirit of FIRST,"},{"time":500000,"text":"gracious professionalism, they are quite proud of this,"},{"time":502000,"text":"so they decide to share a drink."},{"time":505000,"text":"This is a non-trivial thing to do, by the way."},{"time":508000,"text":"Imagine doing that with a wooden stick and a hook on the end of it,"},{"time":511000,"text":"doing either of those."},{"time":513000,"text":"Now Chuck is doing something quite extraordinary,"},{"time":516000,"text":"at least for my limited physical skill."},{"time":521000,"text":"And now he's going to do what DARPA asked me for."},{"time":524000,"text":"He's going to pick up a grape -- he didn't drop it,"},{"time":526000,"text":"he didn't break it --"},{"time":529000,"text":"and he's going to eat it."},{"time":532000,"text":"So, that's where we were"},{"time":534000,"text":"at the end of about 15 months."},{"time":536000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":548000,"text":"But, as I've learned from Richard,"},{"time":551000,"text":"the technology, the processors, the sensors, the motors,"},{"time":556000,"text":"is not the story."},{"time":560000,"text":"I hadn't dealt with this kind of problem"},{"time":563000,"text":"or frankly, this whole segment"},{"time":566000,"text":"of the medical world."},{"time":568000,"text":"I'll give you some astounding things that have happened"},{"time":571000,"text":"as we started this."},{"time":574000,"text":"After we were pretty much convinced we had a good design,"},{"time":578000,"text":"and we'd have to make all the standard engineering trade-offs you always make --"},{"time":581000,"text":"you can always get three out of four of anything you want;"},{"time":584000,"text":"the weight, the size, the cost, the functionality --"},{"time":587000,"text":"I put a bunch of guys in my plane"},{"time":589000,"text":"and I said, \"We're flying down to Walter Reed, and we're going talk to these kids,"},{"time":592000,"text":"because frankly it doesn't matter whether we like this arm."},{"time":594000,"text":"It doesn't matter whether the"},{"time":596000,"text":"Department of Defense likes this arm.\""},{"time":598000,"text":"When I told them that they weren't entirely enthusiastic,"},{"time":601000,"text":"but I told them, \"It really doesn't matter what their opinion is."},{"time":604000,"text":"There is only one opinion that matters,"},{"time":606000,"text":"the kids that are either going to use it or not.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":610000,"text":"I told a bunch of my engineers, \"Look we're going to walk into Walter Reed,"},{"time":613000,"text":"and you're going to see people, lots of them,"},{"time":617000,"text":"missing major body parts."},{"time":619000,"text":"They're probably going to be angry, depressed, frustrated."},{"time":624000,"text":"We're probably going to have to give them support, encouragement."},{"time":627000,"text":"But we've got to extract from them"},{"time":630000,"text":"enough information to make sure we're doing the right thing.\""},{"time":635000,"text":"We walked into Walter Reed and I could not have been more wrong."},{"time":640000,"text":"We did see a bunch of people,"},{"time":642000,"text":"a lot of them missing a lot of body parts,"},{"time":646000,"text":"and parts they had left were burned;"},{"time":648000,"text":"half a face gone, an ear burned off."}]},{"cues":[{"time":655000,"text":"They were sitting at a table. They were brought together for us."},{"time":657000,"text":"And we started asking them all questions."},{"time":659000,"text":"\"Look,\" I'd say to them, \"We're not quite as good as nature yet."},{"time":662000,"text":"I could give you fine motor control,"},{"time":665000,"text":"or I could let you curl 40 pounds;"},{"time":667000,"text":"I probably can't do both."},{"time":669000,"text":"I can give you fast control"},{"time":671000,"text":"with low reduction ratios in these gears,"},{"time":673000,"text":"or I can give you power;"},{"time":675000,"text":"I can't give you both."},{"time":677000,"text":"And we were trying to get them to all help us"},{"time":680000,"text":"know what to give them."},{"time":683000,"text":"Not only were they enthusiastic, they kept thinking"},{"time":685000,"text":"they're there to help us."},{"time":687000,"text":"\"Well, would it help if I ...\""},{"time":689000,"text":"\"Guys, and woman,"},{"time":692000,"text":"you've given enough."},{"time":694000,"text":"We're here to help you. We need data. We need to know"},{"time":696000,"text":"what you need.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":699000,"text":"After a half an hour, maybe, there was one guy at the far end of the table"},{"time":702000,"text":"who wasn't saying much."},{"time":704000,"text":"You could see he was missing an arm."},{"time":706000,"text":"He was leaning on his other arm."},{"time":709000,"text":"I called down to the end, \"Hey, you haven't said much."},{"time":711000,"text":"If we needed this or this, what would you want?\""},{"time":714000,"text":"And he said, \"You know,"},{"time":718000,"text":"I'm the lucky guy at this table."},{"time":720000,"text":"I lost my right arm,"},{"time":722000,"text":"but I'm a lefty.\""},{"time":724000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":725000,"text":"So, he wouldn't say much."},{"time":727000,"text":"He had a great spirit, like all the rest of them had great spirits."},{"time":731000,"text":"And he made a few comments."},{"time":733000,"text":"And then the meeting ended. We said goodbye to all these guys."},{"time":736000,"text":"And that guy pushed himself back from the table ..."},{"time":739000,"text":"he has no legs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":745000,"text":"So, we left."},{"time":748000,"text":"And I was thinking,"},{"time":751000,"text":"\"We didn't give them support and encouragement;"},{"time":754000,"text":"they gave it to us."},{"time":757000,"text":"They're not finished giving yet.\""},{"time":760000,"text":"It was astounding."},{"time":763000,"text":"So, we went back."},{"time":765000,"text":"And I started working harder, faster."},{"time":771000,"text":"Then we went out to Brooke Army Medical Center."},{"time":775000,"text":"And we saw lots of these kids, lots of them."},{"time":779000,"text":"And it was astounding"},{"time":781000,"text":"how positive they are."},{"time":785000,"text":"So, we went back,"},{"time":788000,"text":"and we've been working harder yet."},{"time":790000,"text":"We're in clinical trials,"},{"time":792000,"text":"we've got five of them on people."},{"time":794000,"text":"We're screaming along."},{"time":796000,"text":"And I get a call and we go back"},{"time":799000,"text":"to Washington."}]},{"cues":[{"time":802000,"text":"We go back to Walter Reed,"},{"time":804000,"text":"and a kid, literally,"},{"time":807000,"text":"20 some-odd days before that"},{"time":810000,"text":"was blown up."},{"time":814000,"text":"And they shipped him to Germany"},{"time":816000,"text":"and 24 hours later they shipped him from Germany"},{"time":819000,"text":"to Walter Reed."},{"time":823000,"text":"And he was there,"},{"time":825000,"text":"and they said we needed to come."},{"time":827000,"text":"And I went down"},{"time":829000,"text":"and they rolled him into a room."},{"time":833000,"text":"He's got no legs."},{"time":835000,"text":"He's got no arms."},{"time":837000,"text":"He's got a small residual limb on one side."},{"time":840000,"text":"Half of his face is gone,"},{"time":843000,"text":"but they said his vision is coming back."},{"time":846000,"text":"He had one good eye."},{"time":849000,"text":"His name is Brandon Marrocco."}]},{"cues":[{"time":852000,"text":"And he said,"},{"time":855000,"text":"\"I need your arms,"},{"time":857000,"text":"but I need two of them.\""},{"time":860000,"text":"\"You'll get them.\""},{"time":862000,"text":"This kid was from Staten Island."},{"time":865000,"text":"And he said, \"I had a truck,"},{"time":867000,"text":"before I went over there,"},{"time":869000,"text":"and it had a stick."},{"time":872000,"text":"You think I'll be able to drive it?\""},{"time":874000,"text":"\"Sure.\""},{"time":876000,"text":"And I turned around and went, \"How are we going to do this?\""},{"time":878000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":879000,"text":"Anyway, he was just like all the rest of them."},{"time":883000,"text":"He doesn't really want a lot."},{"time":885000,"text":"He wants to help. He told me that"},{"time":887000,"text":"he wanted to go back"},{"time":889000,"text":"to help his buddies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":894000,"text":"So, I was on my way out here."},{"time":897000,"text":"I was asked to stop at Texas."},{"time":901000,"text":"There were 3,500 people,"},{"time":903000,"text":"the Veteran's Administration,"},{"time":905000,"text":"U.S. ... just 3,500 at this huge event"},{"time":908000,"text":"to help the families"},{"time":911000,"text":"of all the kids --"},{"time":915000,"text":"some that have died, some that are"},{"time":917000,"text":"like Brandon --"},{"time":919000,"text":"and they wanted me to speak."},{"time":921000,"text":"I said, \"What am I going to say?"},{"time":923000,"text":"This is not a happy thing. Look, if this happens to you,"},{"time":925000,"text":"I can give you ... This stuff is"},{"time":927000,"text":"still not as good at the original equipment.\""},{"time":932000,"text":"\"You need to come.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":934000,"text":"So, I went."},{"time":936000,"text":"And, as I think you get the point,"},{"time":939000,"text":"there were a lot people there recovering."},{"time":942000,"text":"Some further along than others."},{"time":945000,"text":"But universally, these people that had been through this"},{"time":948000,"text":"had astounding attitudes,"},{"time":951000,"text":"and just the fact that people care"},{"time":956000,"text":"makes a huge difference to them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":959000,"text":"I'll shut up, except one message"},{"time":966000,"text":"or concern I have."},{"time":968000,"text":"I don't think anybody does it intentionally,"},{"time":972000,"text":"but there were people there literally talking about,"},{"time":974000,"text":"\"Well, how much will they get?\""},{"time":979000,"text":"You know, this country is involved as we've all heard,"},{"time":981000,"text":"in this great healthcare debate."},{"time":985000,"text":"\"Who is entitled to what?"},{"time":988000,"text":"Who is entitled to how much?"},{"time":990000,"text":"Who is going to pay for it?\""},{"time":994000,"text":"Those are tough questions."},{"time":996000,"text":"I don't have an answer to that. Not everybody"},{"time":998000,"text":"can be entitled to everything simply because you were born here."},{"time":1001000,"text":"It's not possible. It would be nice"},{"time":1003000,"text":"but let's be realistic."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1005000,"text":"They were tough questions. There's polarized groups down there."},{"time":1007000,"text":"I don't know the answers."},{"time":1010000,"text":"There are other questions that are tough."},{"time":1012000,"text":"\"Should we be there?"},{"time":1014000,"text":"How do we get out?"},{"time":1016000,"text":"What do we need to do?\" There's very polarized"},{"time":1018000,"text":"answers to that question too,"},{"time":1019000,"text":"and I don't have any answers to that."},{"time":1023000,"text":"Those are political questions, economic questions,"},{"time":1025000,"text":"strategic questions."},{"time":1029000,"text":"I don't have the answer. But let me give you a simple"},{"time":1032000,"text":"concern or maybe statement, then."},{"time":1037000,"text":"It is an easy answer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1040000,"text":"I know what these kids deserve"},{"time":1043000,"text":"on the healthcare side."},{"time":1046000,"text":"I was talking to one of them,"},{"time":1049000,"text":"and he was really liking this arm --"},{"time":1051000,"text":"it's way, way, way better than a plastic"},{"time":1054000,"text":"stick with a hook on it --"},{"time":1057000,"text":"but there's nobody in this room that would rather have that"},{"time":1059000,"text":"than the one you got."},{"time":1063000,"text":"But I was saying to him, \"You know,"},{"time":1065000,"text":"the first airplane"},{"time":1067000,"text":"went 100 feet in 1903."},{"time":1070000,"text":"Wilbur and Orville."},{"time":1073000,"text":"But you know what? It wouldn't have made an old pigeon jealous."},{"time":1076000,"text":"But now we got Eagles out there,"},{"time":1079000,"text":"F15s, even that Bald Eagle."},{"time":1084000,"text":"I've never seen a bird flying around at Mach 2."},{"time":1088000,"text":"I think eventually we'll make these things extraordinary.\""},{"time":1093000,"text":"And I said to that kid,"},{"time":1095000,"text":"\"I'll stop when your buddies"},{"time":1098000,"text":"are envious of your Luke arm"},{"time":1102000,"text":"because of what it can do, and how it does it."},{"time":1105000,"text":"And we'll keep working. And I'm not going to stop working"},{"time":1108000,"text":"until we do that.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1111000,"text":"And I think this country"},{"time":1114000,"text":"ought to continue its great debate,"},{"time":1116000,"text":"whining and complaining, \"I'm entitled.\" \"You're a victim.\""},{"time":1120000,"text":"And whining and complaining about what our foreign policy ought to be."},{"time":1123000,"text":"But while we have the luxury of whining and complaining about"},{"time":1126000,"text":"who's paying for what and how much we get,"},{"time":1129000,"text":"the people that are out there"},{"time":1131000,"text":"giving us that great privilege of whining and complaining,"},{"time":1133000,"text":"I know what they deserve:"},{"time":1135000,"text":"everything humanly possible."},{"time":1138000,"text":"And we ought to give it to them."},{"time":1140000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}